2.plot: Welcome back to Area 31! Today we're fortifying our base and doing some masterful construction. We don't know who or what is out there. Might as well be prepared.

3.title: Clip: transportation time
3.plot: Welcome back to area 31. We have power but now we're trying to expand.

4.title: Clip: goodbye home
4.plot: They found out where we are. I was so stupid. Well, time to find a new home sweet home.

5.title: Clip: zombie!
5.plot: Welcome back to area 31. Today we're exploring the nearby dungeons.

6.title: Clip: dungeons
6.plot: Today on area 31 we continue our dungeon delve. Look at all the cool stuff we found.

7.title: Clip: locked on
7.plot: Today we're making missiles to defend ourselves.

8.title: Clip: happy birthday
8.plot: Okay. So. Our missile didn't work. Let's fix that. Also, it's my birthday.

9.title: Clip: tycerx has been found
9.plot: Tycerx has been discovered. Let's go pay him a visit.

10.title: Clip: tycerx needs help
10.plot: Welcome back to area 31. We hear some people are teaming up and one of our friends needs help.

11.title: Clip: tycerx's reply
11.plot: Today we're going to see if tycerx replied to our offer.

12.title: Clip: power armor upgrades
12.plot: Look at these new power upgrades to our armor.

13.title: Clip: light speed running
13.plot: Today we're the flash. Ok well not literally but we can run so freaking fast.

14.title: Clip: i meet tycerx
14.plot: Today we're meeting tycerx for the first time in the game. It could be great, or it could go badly.

15.title: Clip: fallout pixel painters
15.plot: Join cory, nick, uni and adam as they embark on a painting journey unlike any other.

16.title: Clip: god sword
16.plot: Today we're giving a huge power upgrade to our rapier.

17.title: Clip: epic battle in minecraft area 31
17.plot: Today we're making a new sword. We also explore the twilight forest. You would not believe what we found there.

18.title: Clip: over powered bossi
18.plot: We're back in the twilight forest to explore a fortress and we find an almost invincible boss.

19.title: Clip: eliminate tycer
19.plot: Today we found out how to kill the lich, and it's not going to happen right now. But tycer is planning to betray me.

20.title: Clip: intruder alert in minecraft area 31
20.plot: Today we go back to the twilight forest to find the mushroom kingdom and take on a lich.

21.title: Clip: the bomb
21.plot: There's a bomb in my base. Tycer booby trapped my base for revenge. War has been declared.

22.title: Clip: nuclear item in minecraft area 31
22.plot: Today we're going to test launch a nuke that we're going to send to tycerx.

23.title: Clip: minecraft area 31- what's that!
23.plot: Through random numbers we discovered someone else's base we can teleport to.
